                <summary>Another volunteer company was recently organized and elected the men listed
                    above as officers. It numbers sixty men, but the members hope to increase it to
                    one hundred. Professor J. Hotchkiss is also in the process of raising another
                    company that will go into service after the harvest. It will be composed largely
                    of farm boys who cannot leave until after the crops have been gathered.</summary>
                <note/>
                <look/>
